    "---\n",
    "## Part 2 \u2014 Traversal Definitions (~10 min)\n",
    "\n",
    "For each traversal, describe the **order** in which root, left subtree, and right subtree are visited. Type your answer as three words separated by commas, e.g. `left, root, right`. Just use the plain words \"left\", \"root\", \"right\" \u2014 no need for full sentences like \"visit the left subtree first.\" The order you list them in is what's graded.\n",
    "\n",
    "**Fill in 2a\u20132c below, then run the checker cell at the end of Part 2.**"
   ]
  },
